Risperidone
===========

Libre and open-source roblox game finder tailored to find games
that has similar feature, style or even gameplay.

RISPERIDONE IS UNDER ACTIVE DEVELOPMENT, PLEASE EXPECT THE GAME
TO BE UNEXPECTEDLY SHUT DOWN (I DO NOT HAVE MONEY TO DEPLOY THE
SOFTWARE)

You can find the source code on GitHub <https://github.com/youkwhd/Risperidone>
this tool will always and forever be libre and updated.

Related discovery tools: better discovery, obscure game finder,
surreal game finder.

Prerequisite
------------

Required for external Roblox development:

    - aftman <https://github.com/LPGhatguy/aftman>
    - lune <https://github.com/lune-org/lune>
    - rojo <https://github.com/rojo-rbx/rojo>

Installation
------------

You only need to do this only once:

    aftman install

Building
--------

Build and save rbxl place:

    rojo build -o Risperidone.rbxl

Synchronize
-----------

To get the latest Workspace (map):

    lune run scripts/sync.luau

Spawn a rojo server:

    rojo serve

Then connect to the server from Roblox Studio <https://rojo.space/docs/v7/getting-started/installation/#installing-the-plugin>.
